description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 68, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 136, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 1 for East, 1 for South, and 2 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40682-31122-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [136 Votes, Top 15% Score]
